###Base 64 
they usually end with = or ==
**to encode
base64 my.txt > your.txt # your.txt is the ouput file coded
echo "Elodie" | base64  #this will encode elodie

**decode
base64 -d your.png > they.png #they is the output decoded file
echo "ZWxvZGllCg==" | base64 -d #decode
echo "ZWxvZGllCg==" | base64 --decode # --decode works also 

